transcript.text: This video is about shipping markup over shipping cost.
You can put default markup percentage.
Also you can change percentage markup with condition if shipping cost is high.
Sometimes it's critical when markup is a higher percentage and shipping price is also high.
In that condition total shipping cost is too big.
To avoid that, we introduced markup rule over shipping.
Put conditional amount, change markup percentage.
If you have any queries, please contact us at support@onprintshop.com.

ocr.text: Go to Settings to activate Windows.
A Home > Shipping Method > Shipping Configuration Markup
